Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.03,0:01:24.84,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Podľa mestskej legendy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:27.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}deti, ktoré zaspia s kyberokuliarmi na nose
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:30.88,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}prejdú na „druhú stranu“.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:39.51,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tu som už predtým bola...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.51,0:01:40.44,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{fade this voice?} Juko...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:43.67,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Juko...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.06,0:01:46.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dávaj si pozor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:47.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Juko...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.51,0:01:50.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Si veľmi blízko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:52.82,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Počkaj! Kto si?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:53.79,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uteč!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.79,0:01:55.85,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo znamená 4-4-2-3?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:57.05,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Juko,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:01:58.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}musíš ujsť!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:00.22,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rýchlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:02.62,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Počkaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.82,0:02:12.65,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:19.28,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rýchlo, rýchlo! Prídete neskoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:21.42,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jasako!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:22.28,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dobré ráno!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:29.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Skoro som prišla neskoro v posledný deň školského roku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:37.48,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej ty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.48,0:02:39.22,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo tu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:41.97,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...robíš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:44.97,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vďaka za odvoz, teta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:46.47,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haraken!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:47.90,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vďaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:52.03,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pre teba všetko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.52,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:57.24,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej vy tam!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:57.87,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Áno?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:02:59.53,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kde je tu parkovisko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.03,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, ehm... tam!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:08.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isako!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:10.16,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Toto je náš včerajší zisk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:16.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je úžasné, Isako!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:19.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kedy ma už prestanete volať Isako?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:22.30,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mimochodom, mám tu pre teba toto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:25.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Platinová vstupenka na letný festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:27.18,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.47,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ty nevieš?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:30.01,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je to špeciálny lístok,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:33.44,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}na ktorý máš všetky atrakcie zadarmo: od lovu zlatých rybiek až po strelnicu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:35.03,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je vážne...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:36.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...úžasné!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:41.17,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Videla som ho znova na križovatke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:43.11,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Možno mi neveríš, Keniči,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:46.63,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ale ja si myslím, že to bol Kuroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:50.62,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Chcem, aby si tam zajtra šiel a presvedčil sa na vlastné oči.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:53.12,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo na to povieš?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:56.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stretneme sa pri svätyni Kajano.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:00.78,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tak toto je Juko Amasawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:04.63,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Presťahovala sa sem pred dvoma týždňami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.72,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Za ten čas stihla spôsobiť dosť problémov.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A tu je ďalšia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:15.15,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ktorá z nich dvoch vytvorila dieru na stanici?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:21.02,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vedela som to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:22.47,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je tu zastaralý Priestor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je dosť veľký.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:28.03,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Idem ho preskúmať.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:43.04,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A ešte niekto sa sem nedávno presťahoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:47.11,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Má rovnaké priezvisko ako môj šéf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.80,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No skvelé! Šéfova dcéra!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:53.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Veci sa komplikujú.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:02.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Poči,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:03.86,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1} bol to signál kirabugu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:10.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Radšej tam dám ešte jeden, len pre prípad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.84,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}K-kto ste?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:24.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No teda, pani učiteľka Maiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:26.51,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja som Harakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:27.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:28.72,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.36,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vy ste príbuzná Harakawu z Biologického krúžku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:32.33,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Áno, presne tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:33.83,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Už sme sa videli.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.72,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ach, myslíte vtedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:37.09,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prepáčte, že som to prehnala s pitím.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.09,0:05:38.09,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tak veľmi sa za to hanbím!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:39.17,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:42.85,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mimochodom, som tu služobne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.01,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hľadala som priestorové abnormality
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.45,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}a našla som nejaké odchýlky v telocvični.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prevediete ma tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:50.03,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:51.55,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}V tom prípade...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.15,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Poďte za mnou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:58.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jeden chybný pohyb a odhalila by ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:05:59.79,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Možno by som mala vytvoriť rušenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:01.79,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Za posledné dva roky
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:06.26,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}vzrástol počet automobilových nehôd detí.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:12.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Preto nikdy nenoste okuliare na ulici.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:16.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Už zase hádže vinu na okuliare.{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:18.13,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fumie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:20.73,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Myslíš si, že to učitelia vidia rovnako?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:21.56,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo také?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.95,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Že Kanna zomrela vlastnou vinou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Určite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:31.36,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haraken trpel celý rok sám.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:34.33,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Teraz už viem, prečo bol stále taký skleslý.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:35.89,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aj ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:39.16,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dáme do toho výskumu všetko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:46.65,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Toto je šéfova dcéra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.03,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A tá druhá...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:06:59.30,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tá ženská...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:01.56,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo chce na záverečnom ceremoniáli?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.02,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:05.18,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pýtala som sa na ňu ocka
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:07.71,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}a ak sa nemýlim, pracuje v jeho oddelení.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:08.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:12.21,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vieš, že môj ocko pracuje pre Megamass, firmu na výrobu okuliarov.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:15.62,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ale momentálne robí na mestskej samospráve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:18.35,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je ale náhoda!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:22.12,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Potom to otrasné meno „Sačči“...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.85,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...vymyslel pravdepodobne ocko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:27.24,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A to platí aj pre „Ja Sačči!“.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.43,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}V-vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:31.63,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pozri sa tam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:34.04,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tá pani je Kannina mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:38.41,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Utíšte sa, prosím!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:47.11,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:49.49,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Teta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dlho sme sa nevideli.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:52.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako sa ti darí?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:53.56,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ešte stále sa ti točieva hlava?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:54.89,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Už som v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:57.12,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}V poslednej dobe sa to stáva len zriedka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:02.66,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Neviete, čo bolo v policajnej správe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:06.52,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Povedali, že kybernavi nemohol spraviť chybu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:12.17,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Podľa všetkého si myslia, že na vine bola nejakým spôsobom Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:17.74,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rozhodla som sa, že sa odsťahujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:24.30,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mimochodom, chcela som ťa o niečo požiadať.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:26.16,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Toto sú Kannine okuliare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:29.11,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Polícia ich konečne vrátila.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:31.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Chcela som sa na ne pozrieť,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ale zdá, že k nim treba nejaké heslo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:36.43,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bola by som rada, keby sa ti podarilo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:40.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}z nich dostať nejaké užitočné informácie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:41.95,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Môžem si ich nechať?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:47.96,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Som si istá, že Kanna by bola rada, keby si ich mal ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.40,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:53.76,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prečo tam Kanna v ten deň bola,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:55.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}čo tam robila,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.63,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}čo cítila.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:08:59.60,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Chcela by som to vedieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:02.92,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dajte mi čas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.92,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Určite vypátram pravdu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:07.35,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}a dám vám vedieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:13.16,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Možno Jasako k nemu niečo cíti.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:14.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:17.28,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let-ný fes-ti-val! Je tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.90,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let-ný fes-ti-val! Je tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:24.46,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dnes bude zá-ba-va, zá-ba-va...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:26.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, bývalý šéfe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:28.52,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prestaň tancovať a poď nám pomôcť.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:29.96,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, presne tak, ex-líder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.98,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Musíme si pohnúť, inak to nestihneme včas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:33.17,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prestaňte s tým „bývalým“!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.90,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}S tréningom sme hotoví.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Poďme sa prichystať na festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:37.66,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ešte nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:40.05,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Š-šéfka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.40,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prečo ešte nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:45.56,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ešte ste nespravili skratku do starej školskej budovy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:49.81,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ale ja sa musím ísť pripraviť na festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:53.19,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo od nás vlastne chceš?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:55.31,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Počas nocovania v škole
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:57.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ich pod zámienkou súboja
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.32,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}vylákate do starej školskej budovy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:02.86,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Po tom, čo ich porazíte im vezmete ich okuliare.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:05.00,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Podrobnosti máte napísané tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:06.99,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Súboj?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:12.09,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Na také detské hry nemáme čas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:14.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zase ma chcete neposlúchnuť?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:16.31,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Počkaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:17.48,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je len nedorozumenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:18.91,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Presne tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:20.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nie je to tak, Daiči?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:24.85,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Potom urobte, čo vám vravím.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:27.35,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nenúťte ma to opakovať!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:31.93,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Daiči.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.36,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo je?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:38.11,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Chcel si byť mojím učňom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:40.74,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ak splníš túto úlohu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:43.48,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}naučím ťa nejaké kódovacie techniky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:44.62,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Naozaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Naozaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:48.38,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ale ak to skazíš...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:51.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}vyhodím ťa z klubu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:52.38,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čože?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:54.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo si o sebe myslí?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:56.33,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je to iba baba a myslí si, že môže rozkazovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:57.57,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Toto je MÔJ klub!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:10:59.95,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako ma chce z neho vyraziť?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.16,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nemôžeme sa jej vzoprieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ešte chvíľu a budeme hotoví.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:05.61,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Spravte to aj za mňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:08.96,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To nie je od teba pekné, Daiči!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:10.62,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako syn predsedu festivalovej komisie
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:13.87,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}musím pomáhať s prípravami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:16.11,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Chceš sa skrátka z tohto uliať!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:18.24,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je festival taký dôležitý?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:21.04,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vy to nechápete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:23.28,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja som dieťa z Tokia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:28.19,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ale správa a oblieka sa ako decká z Daikoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:34.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pátrala po Kuroeho chorobe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:52.82,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mami, vyznáš sa tu v meste?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:54.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:57.19,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}S tvojím otcom sme často chodievali na prechádzky ku stanici.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:59.28,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Predtým ako si sa narodila.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:03.47,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je tu niekde schodisko s mnohými bránami {\i1}torii{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:05.49,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Schodisko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.45,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, to neviem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:12.76,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Už to začalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:14.63,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Konečne ste tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:17.15,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Poďte sem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:18.21,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tak polezte!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:20.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Plán je takýto:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:24.22,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zajtra večer v škole vyzveme Obludu a jej gang na skúšku odvahy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:24.22,Coil Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8}Skúška odvahy je typická detská hra. Po ceste sú nastražené strašidelné prekážky a deti na jej konci musia dokázať, že ich všetky absolvovali.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:28.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Samozrejme, že som nastražil niekoľko pascí.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:30.22,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Potom na nich zaútočíme
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:33.96,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}a donútime ju zaplatiť škodu za naše dvojročné vreckové!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:36.65,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To isté nám kázala urobiť aj Isako.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:37.52,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sklapni!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.74,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Môžeme sa do toho pustiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.49,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ale Isako povedala...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:42.33,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:44.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aby sme na ňu počkali.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:45.90,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:48.28,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pretože nemá dobrý pocit z toho, nechávať to len na tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.03,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čože?! Tá malá...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:51.28,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pozerá sa na mňa zvrchu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.59,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, Daiči!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:55.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tak ty sa ulievaš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:56.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ideš so mnou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:57.48,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To bolí!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:59.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pusť ma, tati!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:16.15,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je to heslo, čo spomínala Kannina mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.98,0:13:26.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haraken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prepáč, že ideme neskoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:36.49,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Deje sa niečo?{\u1}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:38.83,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kde je Fumie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:40.09,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ešte neprišla.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.68,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hovorila, že bude meškať.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:44.77,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:46.84,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prečo si do mňa hodila tie kamene?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:49.84,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo tu robíš, Daiči?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:54.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prišiel som vás vyzvať na súboj.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.35,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Súboj?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:58.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Presne tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:00.23,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kde je Fumie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:01.72,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ešte neprišla.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:02.71,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.86,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tak tu na ňu počkám.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.16,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:10.28,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kjóko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:17.71,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nebudeme tu len tak stáť, poďme si kúpiť limonádu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Skvelý nápad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:19.85,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Teda...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:21.88,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No tak dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:31.86,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo to robíš, ty sopľana!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:36.12,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kjóko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.76,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Povedala som ti, aby si sa nebavila s cudzími ľuďmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:40.78,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mala by si ju hrešiť za niečo iné!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:42.05,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prepáčte, že meškám!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:45.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Konečne si vyliezla, ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:52.03,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prepáčte.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:54.12,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Idem neskoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:55.76,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Daiči!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:56.69,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo je?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.74,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo tu chceš?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:00.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, vieš...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.86,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja som v komisii...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:04.67,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, to je pravda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:08.17,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A prečo si mokrý?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:10.22,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ty si sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:13.81,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Myslím, že Daiči ti chce niečo povedať.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:17.04,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako nehoráznosťou mi chceš zase pokaziť deň?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:26.74,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}N-nechceš si so mnou zahrať futbal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:28.38,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tak nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:32.18,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}N-nechceš ísť so mnou chytať raky?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:33.79,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ani to nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:36.08,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Už viem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:39.60,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nepôjdeš...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:42.65,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...so mnou na letný festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:47.48,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:48.23,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:53.57,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nedáš si so mnou súboj?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.77,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo ti preskočilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:16:00.84,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prečo si nepočkal na Isako a vyzval si ju na súboj?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:02.85,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ešte máme tridsať minút.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:05.09,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sklapni!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:07.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Neznášam, keď mi niekto hovorí, čo mám robiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.82,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vyžmýkal som ti kabát. {happi = short coat}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.86,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nepozerajte sa sem!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:14.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Som zvedavý, čo na to povie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:18.37,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Počkaj polhodinu a poraď sa s ňou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:23.01,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ak ťa to zaujíma, tak o tom súboji som vedela.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:24.68,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:30.88,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ale kto normálny by povedal takú blbosť: "Nedala by si si so mnou súboj?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:32.38,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Určite bol len nervózny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:34.73,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bolo to roztomilé.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:36.13,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:37.01,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo je na ňom roztomilé?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:40.52,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ty to naozaj nechápeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:41.73,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo také?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:43.57,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To si celá ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:48.16,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mám nápad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:49.43,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nápad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:53.15,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Máme asi tridsať minút, kým nás Daiči znova vyzve na súboj.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:55.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nepôjdeme sa zatiaľ zabaviť?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:56.78,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dnes je predsa festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:17:00.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jasako, nehovor také hlúposti.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:02.04,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No tak, no tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:31.72,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:32.99,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sopliak jeden!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:34.16,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kam to mieriš?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:35.32,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prepáčte...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:38.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Musíš ju držať vo vodorovnej polohe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:41.92,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Žiadne napätie...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:45.42,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isako sa na vodcu hodí omnoho viac ako Daiči.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:48.78,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, ale aj tak jej neverím.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:49.78,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Neveríš?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:52.92,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nevyžadujem vernosť,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.23,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}len, aby ste urobili to, čo vám poviem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:02.63,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isako...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:03.88,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo je?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:04.73,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Deje sa niečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:06.60,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nie, nič.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:06.60,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nie, nič.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.89,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tak, môžete ich vyzvať na súboj.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:11.61,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, to vlastne...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:27.72,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takto to ďalej nejde.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:28.23,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo je?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:29.65,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Musím na záchod!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:31.17,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, Daiči!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:32.84,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kam ideš?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:35.19,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A to som chcela...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:37.83,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Na.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:39.17,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:48.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:49.69,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Presne ako som si myslela!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.49,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo je?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:53.18,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Presne ako som predpokladala.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:55.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}S vami dvoma to bude jednoduchšie ako s Fumie a Daičim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:56.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}O čom to hovoríš?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.57,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Si zlá, Aiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:00.00,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Že?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:05.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo tam robí?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:07.69,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Súboj...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:09.08,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Znamená...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.45,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Láska...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:11.45,Coil Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}„Hatašiai“ znamená súboj, ale Daiči píše znak „ai“, čo v kandži znamená „stretnúť sa“, ale aj „láska“.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:21.47,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Na chvíľu nás nechajte.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.85,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Môžem ju zavolať kedykoľvek.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:28.32,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Koho?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:30.02,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mičiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:34.49,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dokážem vyvolať slečnu Mičiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:37.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A čo má byť?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:41.70,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mohla by som ju zavolať, aby mi pomohla ukradnúť tým deckám okuliare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:46.00,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ale myslím, že bude lepšie, ak to spravíš ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:50.45,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jediné, čo chcem je, aby si im vzal okuliare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:54.13,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:59.12,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kde si bol?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:00.06,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Na, tu máš.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:03.63,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Milión jenov.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:07.01,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ale im to spolu svedčí.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.33,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Potrebujú len trocha postrčiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:12.52,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kam zmizol Haraken?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:20.05,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mohla by si na chvíľu postrážiť Kjóko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:21.03,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.31,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ten hlas...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:31.70,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:33.35,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Harake...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:39.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ilegál!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:49.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To bolo tesné!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:53.82,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je ti niečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:59.57,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zbožňujem festivaly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:02.23,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Spomínaš si, Daiči?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:06.45,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Keď sme boli tretiaci, ponúkol si mi platinový lístok.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:10.20,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dobre sme sa vtedy bavili, ako dnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:12.45,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Neviem, prečo ma to teraz napadlo,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:15.40,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ale bola to zábava.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:19.60,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kam pôjdeme teraz?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.06,0:21:20.87,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sú-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:21.48,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sú?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:24.52,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Súboj...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:26.47,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nezabudni na súboj!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:31.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:35.60,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja ťa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:38.60,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...nenávidím!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:44.43,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ide za nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:45.53,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Utečme!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.12,0:22:03.05,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haraken!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:10.81,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haraken, to je nebezpečné!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:19.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:21.11,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Si to ty, Kuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.35,0:22:31.40,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.42,0:22:38.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:41.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zajtra večer v škole
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:42.80,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}si dáme skúšku odvahy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:44.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To bude náš súboj!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.85,0:22:46.91,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A o čo hráme?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:47.79,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}O okuliare.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.37,0:22:51.63,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ten, kto prehrá, nebude nosiť okuliare do konca prázdnin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:54.65,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je skutočná výzva.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.65,0:22:56.38,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pravidlá sú jednoduché.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:23:00.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Musíš sa dostať na strechu a nechať tam takéto bábiky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:02.80,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ten, kto ich tam dá najviac, vyhráva.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.80,0:23:05.03,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}T-to bude hračka!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:07.63,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Navrhli sme aj trasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.63,0:23:10.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Počet nástrah je neobmedzený.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:12.24,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Chápem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.24,0:23:15.24,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nastražil som svoje najlepšie pasce.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:18.47,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nemôžem sa dočkať.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.57,0:24:50.86,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nabudúce v Dennou Coil:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.47,0:24:54.22,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Slečna Mičko: Z druhej strany
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.71,0:24:57.01,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tešte sa!
